          "name": "699b",
          "text": "As an all-volunteer organization that leverages technology to inspire greater volunteerism, ServiceSpace aims to facilitate people to take part in these social shifts. In 15 years it has grown to a global network of 400,000 people who volunteer their skills and times to help others. Among the projects that have been incubated in or supported by this network of ServiceSpace volunteers are:",
